column16: Brandon Belt homers (16) on a fly ball to right field.    Joe Panik scores.
Buster Posey called out on strikes.
Joe Panik doubles (16) on a line drive to right fielder Jose Osuna.
Gorkys Hernandez hit by pitch.    Joe Panik to 3rd.    Hunter Pence to 2nd.
Hunter Pence walks.   Joe Panik to 2nd.
Joe Panik singles on a line drive to left fielder John Jaso.
Denard Span grounds out, second baseman Adam Frazier to first baseman Josh Bell.
Steven Souza Jr.   flies out to right fielder Gregory Polanco.
Jesus Sucre singles on a line drive to right fielder Gregory Polanco.
Adeiny Hechavarria flies out to left fielder John Jaso.
Tommy Pham grounds out, third baseman David Freese to first baseman Josh Bell.
Keon Broxton doubles (11) on a ground ball to left fielder Adam Frazier.   Orlando Arcia scores.
Pirates challenged (play at 1st), call on the field was upheld: Orlando Arcia reaches on a missed catch error by first baseman Jose Osuna, assist to shortstop Jordy Mercer.
Tommy La Stella lines out to right fielder Gregory Polanco.
Alexi Amarista singles on a line drive to right fielder Gregory Polanco.   Raimel Tapia scores.    Tony Wolters to 3rd.
Trevor Story flies out to right fielder Gregory Polanco.   Raimel Tapia to 3rd.
Raimel Tapia hits a ground-rule double (2) on a fly ball down the left-field line.
Nolan Arenado grounds out, third baseman Josh Harrison to first baseman Josh Bell.
Tony Wolters grounds into a double play, second baseman Max Moroff to shortstop Jordy Mercer to first baseman Jose Osuna.   Raimel Tapia out at 2nd.
Raimel Tapia walks.   Ian Desmond to 2nd.
Tyler Moore called out on strikes.
Derek Dietrich singles on a ground ball to second baseman Josh Harrison.  T.   Realmuto to 3rd.
J.  T.   Realmuto doubles (9) on a ground ball to left fielder Adam Frazier.   Marcell Ozuna scores.
Marcell Ozuna doubles (12) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Adam Frazier.
Ichiro Suzuki grounds out, first baseman Josh Bell to pitcher Edgar Santana.
